metadata.name: GXF Micro-Slide Fingerprints (Negative OE)
metadata.description: Hybrid GXF Micro-slide Negative contact sheet for community claim. Airdropping to all collectors who have claimed their NFT from the physical slide.  Anyone whom wants to be on my collector's list & doesn't hold this physical, or any NFT of mine make sure to collect at  least one of these to be on my list.  This open edition connects my community virtually & IRL alongside my main Handprint 1/1 on SuperRare, viewable at  https://superrare.com/artwork-v2/handprint-29865
